en-en.name: English from English
en-en.content:
WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.200 --> 00:00:03.360
All right, so here we are, in front of the
elephants

00:00:05.318 --> 00:00:07.974
the cool thing about these guys is that they
have really...

00:00:07.974 --> 00:00:12.616
really really long trunks

00:00:12.616 --> 00:00:14.367
and that's cool

00:00:14.421 --> 00:00:15.733
(baaaaaaaaaaahhh!!)

00:00:16.881 --> 00:00:18.881
and that's pretty much all there is to
say

de-de.name: German from German
de-de.content:
WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: de

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.067
Also hier sind wir vor den Elefanten.

00:00:05.067 --> 00:00:12.467
Das Coole an den Typen ist dass sie sehr, sehr, sehr, lange Rüssel haben.

00:00:12.467 --> 00:00:14.267
Und das ist cool.

00:00:17.067 --> 00:00:21.000
Ansonsten gibt es nicht wirklich viel zu sagen.
